message.body: Hey! I can’t remember if we were going to meet today but I have some kind of chest cold and am gonna stay in and fend it off before it gets worse.
next week?
Oh no! I am sorry to hear that! Let me look at my calendar for next week...
Saturday the 7th works for me
Do you want me to bring you anything ?
Aw thank you. I am OK. Hunter got some stuff at the co-op this morning. It’s not as bad as it could be, I’m just hacking up some junk and tired. If this is the worst of it, I’ll be lucky
Next week for sure though
Rest up! And I will see you next week!
thanks see you soon
￼Love this list!
I almost posted it on Instagram
And the freakin internet at cedar works is not working again :/
Lol so good out of context! We got it to work last time by unplugging for over 4 minutes
Unplugging the router?
Or modem
Yeah. With the ladder
Yuck! What a waste of time
I was just trying to come in and do an hour of work :/
I'm not sure which it actually goes to. It's a black plug/box labeled "Comcast"
Ugh!
I am just going to go home soon
Seems to be working now - at least I was able to download the doc I needed from my email
I wonder if Comcast ever came out...
If it happens again I'm going to send an email. It's happened the last three times
Oh really - maybe it just time to send an email now - it's been 3 weeks !
Yeah. I'll shoot him an email. Wonder what changed.
Cool - thanks - I hope you are getting some rest!
Sound perfect for today!
No probs. I am parked in bed in long johns.
